&lt;p&gt;Bank Band 5 RMN&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Day rate inclusive of HCAA £17.78 per hour&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Saturday &amp; Night rate inclusive of HCAA £22.41 per hour&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Sunday &amp; Bank Holiday rate inclusive of HCAA £27.05 per hour&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are currently recruiting for Staff RMN to join our Bank on an ad-hoc basis throughout Hillingdon and Mount Vernon Sites.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You must have excellent verbal and written communication skills, be able to work under pressure and have a caring and professional attitude. You should be flexible to work across the Trust, reliable and be able to work well as a team.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You must also have 6 months experience working within the NHS.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;As part of the selection process candidates will be required to undertake a short numeracy and literacy test. Please be advised if you are unsuccessful at this stage you will not go forward to an interview.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Our vision is&quot;To put compassionate care, safety and quality at the heart of everything we do.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
